1
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:31,480
Xiao Jingyi!

2
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:39,799
You bitch!

3
00:00:40,399 --> 00:00:41,000
It's all your fault!

4
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:43,399
You ruined all my plans!

5
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:45,439
You all deserve to die!

6
00:00:46,759 --> 00:00:47,359
Why?

7
00:00:47,799 --> 00:00:49,000
It was my son who died,

8
00:00:49,079 --> 00:00:49,920
not you!

9
00:00:50,439 --> 00:00:51,719
He's not your son!

10
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:55,719
You don't deserve to be his mother!

11
00:00:58,920 --> 00:01:00,600
You all deserve to die!

12
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:02,759
[The debts of Lady Liu]

13
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:06,400
[shouldn't have been yours to repay.]

14
00:01:07,799 --> 00:01:08,840
[Fate can be cruel.]

15
00:01:09,879 --> 00:01:10,879
[He carried too much]

16
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:12,519
[unbreakable karma.]

17
00:01:16,799 --> 00:01:18,040
[Perhaps only this]

18
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:19,760
[can]

19
00:01:20,439 --> 00:01:21,680
[free him from his obsessions.]

20
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,280
[Everything]

21
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,280
[is like a bubble,]

22
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:28,040
[shattered upon touch.]

23
00:01:31,319 --> 00:01:33,400
[How much torment and grievances]

24
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,680
[have you endured?]

25
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:55,480
[These are all letters of gratitude from the people.]

26
00:01:57,599 --> 00:01:58,719
[I've read them all for you.]

27
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,560
[Some are written in a crooked way,]

28
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,360
[which is quite amusing.]

29
00:02:13,199 --> 00:02:13,800
[And,]

30
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,240
[there are young ladies who can't read,]

31
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,479
[so they drew many pictures for you.]

32
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,000
[You'll surely like them.]

33
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,240
[I've also written to you.]

34
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,759
[If you see it,]

35
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,599
[please come to me in a dream.]

36
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,199
[I have no regrets in this life,]

37
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:44,840
[only hoping for peace in the world,]

38
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,240
[and well-being for all.]

39
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,039
[Yan Ge,]

40
00:02:48,919 --> 00:02:49,599
[forget me.]

41
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,039
Qingdai.

42
00:03:27,719 --> 00:03:29,000
Uncle Yin's body

43
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,680
has been found.

44
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,199
You'd better not see it.

45
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,560
Yin's remains

46
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,840
are incomplete,

47
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,360
with multiple signs of animal gnawing.

48
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,439
His head...

49
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:07,919
The head is also damaged.

50
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:10,360
This was found near the remains.

51
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,040
Father,

52
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,480
can you not go?

53
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:25,279
We can repay the debt together.

54
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,319
The world is in chaos,

55
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,040
to restore order.

56
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:31,000
I don't want you to risk your life.

57
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:32,920
It's not Qingdai's responsibility

58
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,000
to repay the debt.

59
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,560
You should do what you want.

60
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:38,560
The Hu people

61
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,399
have never shown any doubt about me.

62
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,319
But you just said

63
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:43,279
to Mr. Xiao...

64
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,079
You...

65
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,160
It's okay.

66
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:46,680
It's just that businessmen

67
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,480
always make the worst-case preparations.

68
00:04:49,199 --> 00:04:50,600
Don't worry too much.

69
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,079
Really?

70
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,240
Really.

71
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,519
Then,

72
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,040
you must come back safely.

73
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:01,360
Qingdai,

74
00:05:01,519 --> 00:05:03,399
don't you always want Persian fabrics?

75
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:04,800
When I come back,

76
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,639
I'll bring you

77
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,879
the finest Persian brocade.

78
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:08,519
Really?

79
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:11,800
Alright then.

80
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:12,720
Dad,

81
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,879
you must come back safely.

82
00:05:16,199 --> 00:05:16,720
Don't worry,

83
00:05:17,279 --> 00:05:18,399
I will.

84
00:05:48,879 --> 00:05:49,800
I'll handle

85
00:05:51,319 --> 00:05:52,199
the rest.

86
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,199
Don't worry.

87
00:05:55,839 --> 00:05:56,720
Take a good rest.

88
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:19,959
My father...

89
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,199
He told me

90
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:25,319
he would come back.

91
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,279
He asked me to wait for him.

92
00:06:30,199 --> 00:06:31,720
He would bring me

93
00:06:32,439 --> 00:06:33,839
the finest brocades

94
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,360
and the jewelry I wanted.

95
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:42,000
He never went to the Women's Clinic.

96
00:06:46,399 --> 00:06:47,160
Yunzhou,

97
00:06:49,759 --> 00:06:51,160
I have no home left.

98
00:06:58,839 --> 00:06:59,319
It's okay.

99
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:02,519
I'll always be with you.

100
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,720
The Xiao's Mansion is your home.

101
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:07,800
This letter

102
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,360
was found in the Yin's Mansion.

103
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:12,800
It seems that my father

104
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,680
had already made the worst preparations.

105
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:19,959
[Qingdai,]

106
00:07:20,519 --> 00:07:21,680
[if you are reading this letter,]

107
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:23,000
[it means I]

108
00:07:23,439 --> 00:07:24,920
[can't come back.]

109
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:26,680
[I raised you to adulthood.]

110
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,600
[Though I can't be with you,]

111
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,720
[I have no regrets.]

112
00:07:31,319 --> 00:07:32,279
[My beloved daughter,]

113
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,279
[follow your heart.]

114
00:07:34,759 --> 00:07:35,319
[Don't rely on others.]

115
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,639
[Don't be trapped.]

116
00:07:37,199 --> 00:07:38,160
[Even in the face of challenges,]

117
00:07:38,439 --> 00:07:39,839
[you can walk your own path.]

118
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:40,959
[Do not grieve,]

119
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:41,959
[do not yearn.]

120
00:07:42,879 --> 00:07:44,199
[May you be well,]

121
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,040
[safe, and joyful.]

122
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,720
[May I be your father]

123
00:07:48,199 --> 00:07:49,319
[in the next life,]

124
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,600
[and hear you call me]

125
00:07:52,399 --> 00:07:53,079
["Father" once more.]

126
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,079
It's okay.

127
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:04,240
I'm here.

128
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:07,720
Father.

129
00:08:13,639 --> 00:08:16,199
By the Emperor's decree:

130
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,600
Chang'an has been struck by plague,

131
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:20,360
leaving the people in dire straits.

132
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:22,160
I am deeply concerned.

133
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:25,639
Thanks to the benevolent heart of the Women's Clinic,

134
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,480
the secret formula of Qibaoyin

135
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,079
and the anti-plague method have been discovered,

136
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:32,639
allowing Chang'an to turn the tide.

137
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,799
Now, a plaque is bestowed

138
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:36,679
to recognize their contribution.

139
00:08:37,279 --> 00:08:38,639
Additionally, a reward of 100 taels of silver

140
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:40,759
is granted for expanding the clinic

141
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,360
and providing more medicine.

142
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,120
Although the plague has subsided,

143
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:46,080
your benevolence remains.

144
00:08:46,759 --> 00:08:47,720
May the people

145
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:50,559
remember the kindness of this clinic

146
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:52,639
and pass it on for generations.

147
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,440
Thank you, Your Majesty.

148
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:04,720
Congratulations!

149
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,639
Congratulations!

150
00:09:05,639 --> 00:09:06,080
Congratulations!

151
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,720
Congratulations!

152
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,120
That's great, Xinyue.

153
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:10,159
Now,

154
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:11,720
we have the money

155
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:13,240
to rebuild the Women's Clinic.

156
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,039
Don't worry.

157
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:16,320
The clinic saved our lives.

158
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:18,080
We must help it.

159
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,440
I will also contribute the wood from my home

160
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:21,399
to help build

161
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:22,279
the clinic.

162
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:23,559
Everyone will help.

163
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:23,960
Yes.

164
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:24,960
We will all lend a hand.

165
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,320
Everyone will come.

166
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:26,960
We will all help.

167
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:30,960
Thank you all.

168
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:32,720
Today,

169
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,159
please go back.

170
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:36,840
We'll be there to help.

171
00:09:45,159 --> 00:09:47,200
Your efforts in the epidemic control

172
00:09:49,759 --> 00:09:51,320
must be remembered.

173
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,159
To the left.

174
00:10:06,639 --> 00:10:07,000
Okay.

175
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:07,840
I'll do it.

176
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:08,759
Yes.

177
00:10:09,039 --> 00:10:09,879
It's too high.

178
00:10:09,919 --> 00:10:10,320
Okay.

179
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:11,919
Hold it.

180
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:12,759
To the left.

181
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,879
Thank you all for your hard work

182
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:17,440
to revive the Women's Clinic.

183
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:18,960
Physician Yin,

184
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:20,200
you're too kind.

185
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:20,960
This is

186
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:21,919
what we should do.

187
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:22,519
Yeah.

188
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,840
Without the Women's Clinic,

189
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:24,879
there wouldn't be us today.

190
00:10:24,879 --> 00:10:25,240
Yes.

191
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,200
Yan Ge,

192
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,120
think it through.

193
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:46,000
I'll continue his path,

194
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:47,679
spreading his and your medical knowledge

195
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:49,480
beyond Chang'an.

196
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,399
Wish you all the best.

197
00:11:07,559 --> 00:11:08,320
Yan Ge,

198
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:13,360
what's wrong?

199
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,799
There's one more important thing.

200
00:11:17,919 --> 00:11:18,679
What is it?

201
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,320
The interview.

202
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,320
The path of medicine is long,

203
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:28,080
but as long as there's light in your heart,

204
00:11:28,559 --> 00:11:30,279
you won't fear the road ahead.
